frames.caption: A vintage steam locomotive travels through a bustling, narrow street lined with historic buildings. The scene is vibrant with autumn leaves and a crowd of people gathered along the tracks. In the background, a grand cathedral towers over the scene, adding a majestic touch.
frames.description: The scene depicts a historical setting where a steam train is making its way through a crowded street in a European-style city. The architecture is gothic, with a towering cathedral and ornate buildings, and the atmosphere is lively with people and autumn foliage.

frames.caption: A steam train billows thick clouds of smoke as it moves through a bustling, historic town. The scene is vibrant with autumn leaves and a crowd of people gathered along the platform. Gothic architecture looms in the background, adding a sense of grandeur and nostalgia.
frames.description: The image depicts a lively scene at a train station in a historic town. A steam train is in motion, surrounded by a crowd of people and set against a backdrop of gothic buildings and autumn foliage.
